COMPUTE SHELL SORT OF (64, 34, 25, 12, 22, 11, 90)
STEP 1: SET GAP = N/2 = 3
STEP 2: INSERTION SORT WITH GAP 3
   COMPARE ELEMENTS 3 APART
   64,12: SWAP -> 12 34 25 64 22 11 90
   34,22: NO SWAP
   25,11: SWAP -> 12 22 25 64 34 11 90
   (CONTINUE...)
STEP 3: SET GAP = 1
STEP 4: STANDARD INSERTION SORT
RESULT: 11 12 22 25 34 64 90
